Package: SNPutils
Title: Convert Genotype Data to Allele Formats and Generate Summary
    Statistics
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Hedia", "Tnani", , "hediatnani0@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-0380-9740"))
Description: Tools for converting numerical genotype data (0, 1, 2) to
    allele pairs, generating TYP and COM file formats, validating allele
    assignments, and calculating sample and variant summary statistics.
